Tips for use:

Make sure this file is readable only by your user:

chmod 600 ~/actools.env

Replace #ReplaceWithStrongPassword with a secure random password. Example:

openssl rand -base64 24
Double-check BASE_DOMAIN and DRUPAL_ADMIN_EMAIL are correct; Caddy uses these for HTTPS.

After saving, run the installer as:

sudo ./actools.sh fresh
